OL,3,CSeaham celebrates much-loved WWI Tommy
OL,4,Cstatue's tenth anniversary
OL,6,FA service has been held to mark the
OL,7,Ftenth anniversary of Seaham's much-
OL,8,Floved Tommy statue.
OL,10,F'Tommy' - a statue erected to
OL,11,Fcommemorate those who fought in the
OL,12,FFirst World War - is marking a decade
OL,13,Fof overlooking the County Durham coast.
OL,15,FThe sculpture, created by Ray
OL,16,FLonsdale, has become a popular North
OL,17,FEast landmark in its own right.
